DeathSteel::

He had been sitting in his quarters for a while as was feeling as if 
he was being shelved. He left his room and went walking towards the 
command deck. He hoped he would run into Kaiser. He wanted to 
congratulate him on the fight. Kaiser was a very formitable opponant. 
He also wanted to try to see how he could manage to move up in the 
ranks of this group. Perhaps he would one day obtain a high position 
and then he could put his plan to work.
